seo: Nacos,身份认证绕过,JWT,默认密钥,漏洞检测
seo_en: Nacos, authentication bypass, JWT, default secret key, vulnerability detection
summary: 该插件用于检测Nacos版本低于2.2.0时存在的默认JWT Token认证绕过漏洞，可提取用户信息或创建新用户。
summary_en: This plugin detects the default JWT Token authentication bypass vulnerability in Nacos versions below 2.2.0, allowing extraction of user information or creation of new users.
